cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.DS 

This paper deals with classification problems and evaluation metrics, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the impact of class imbalance on evaluation, which is a security concern (cs.CR) and a data science issue (cs.DS).
